<lb n="0899a23" ed="T"/><note place="inline">七</note>娑<note place="inline">引</note>囉&CB00425;底<note place="inline">八</note>達那&CB00425;底<note place="inline">九</note>蘇囉&CB00425;底<note place="inline">十</note>阿梨
