<lb n="0899a29" ed="T"/>三滿多薩囉&CB00425;梨<note place="inline">引三十</note>珂薩哩<note place="inline">引三十一</note>阿<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00085;哩多
<pb n="0899b" id="T21.1377.0899b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0899b01" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合三十二</note>摩賀<note place="inline">引</note><note n="0899004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00085;＝縛【元】</note><app n="0899004"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">縛</rdg></app>哩多<note place="inline">二合三十三</note>竭&CB00135;<note place="inline">引三十四</note>彌<note place="inline">引</note>珂
<lb n="0899b02" ed="T"/>梨<note place="inline">引三十<note n="0899005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">五＋（達）【元】</note><app n="0899005"><lem wit="【大】">五</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">五達</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0899b03" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0899b0301">佛言阿難。我此宣說寶帶大明有大功德。若
<lb n="0899b04" ed="T"/>有持是明者。隨諸所求皆得圓滿。所有持明
<lb n="0899b05" ed="T"/>天眾部多眾。吠多拏眾大力天眾。諸神通精
<lb n="0899b06" ed="T"/>進仙眾。於持明者不能為障。阿難當知今此
<lb n="0899b07" ed="T"/>寶帶大明。諸佛世尊共所宣說。普為一切眾
<lb n="0899b08" ed="T"/>生利益安樂。乃至於一切處密作擁護。阿難
<lb n="0899b09" ed="T"/>大地所有大惡難調攝人威光者極惡業者。
<lb n="0899b10" ed="T"/>若方若隅乃至一切處。聞是寶帶大明時皆
<lb n="0899b11" ed="T"/>大驚怖。又此大明周匝十由旬內。能為一切
<lb n="0899b12" ed="T"/>眾生而作擁護。救諸難事攝持護念。令諸眾
<lb n="0899b13" ed="T"/>生息災安樂。不為杖打不為<note n="0899006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">刀＝兵【三】</note><note n="0899006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">刀＝兵【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0899006"><lem wit="【大】">刀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">兵</rdg></app>傷不為毒中。
<lb n="0899b14" ed="T"/>一切惡毒自然消滅。惡友遠離一切惡者。作
<lb n="0899b15" ed="T"/>禁縛事自然解脫。若人及非人。欲於一切眾
<lb n="0899b16" ed="T"/>生作惱害者。應當依法建立壇場。以諸香華
<lb n="0899b17" ed="T"/>供養如來。依法結界沐浴清淨。誦是寶帶大
<lb n="0899b18" ed="T"/>明。彼諸惡者自然攝伏不能為害。乃至一切
<lb n="0899b19" ed="T"/>病苦亦得息除。復說大明曰。</p>
<lb n="0899b20" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0899b2001" type="dharani">怛&CB00853;<note place="inline">切身下同</note>他<note place="inline">引<note n="0899007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔一〕－【元】</note><app n="0899007"><lem wit="【大】">一</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">&lac;</rdg></app><app source="0899003" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">句</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app></note>&CB00135;<note n="0899008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00848;＝梨【明】＊</note><note n="0899008" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="＊"/>&CB00848;＝梨【明】＊</note><app n="0899008"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00848;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">梨</rdg></app>&CB00135;&CB00848;<anchor id="fxT21p0899b02"/><note place="inline">二</note>尾摩梨<note place="inline">引三</note>多摩
<lb n="0899b21" ed="T"/>梨<note place="inline">引四</note>虎唧虎唧<note place="inline">五</note>悉哩<note place="inline">六</note>底哩<note place="inline">七</note>薩梨<note place="inline">引</note>囉<note place="inline">八</note></p>
<lb n="0899b22" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0899b2201">復次阿難又此大明有大功德。說是大明時。
<lb n="0899b23" ed="T"/>若鬼眾聞者驚怖戰掉。若天眾聞者悉來集
<lb n="0899b24" ed="T"/>會。若龍王若部多王聞者亦悉來集。若梵王
<lb n="0899b25" ed="T"/>帝釋大自在天童子天等。聞是大明者皆從
<lb n="0899b26" ed="T"/>異處咸來集此。稱讚隨喜寶帶大明。</p>
<lb n="0899b27" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0899b2701">爾時慈氏菩薩摩訶薩。白佛言世尊。我亦為
<lb n="0899b28" ed="T"/>羅&CB00264;羅童子及一切眾生。作擁護法救諸難
<lb n="0899b29" ed="T"/>事。攝持護念息災安樂。刀杖諸毒不能為害。
<pb n="0899c" id="T21.1377.0899c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0899c01" ed="T"/>惡友禁縛自然遠離。以是利益故隨喜宣說
<lb n="0899c02" ed="T"/>寶帶大明曰。</p>
<lb n="0899c03" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0899c0301" type="dharani">怛&CB00853;他<note place="inline">引一<app source="0899003" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">句</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app></note>阿&CB00085;那<note place="inline">引</note>底<note place="inline">二</note>&CB00425;那<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00135;<note place="inline">三</note>阿尼那
<lb n="0899c04" ed="T"/><note place="inline">引</note>努<note place="inline">四</note>祖盧祖盧<note place="inline">五</note><note n="0899009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">鳴＝烏【三】</note><note n="0899009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鳴＝烏【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0899009"><lem wit="【大】">鳴</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">烏</rdg></app>哩馱<note place="inline">二合</note>難尼<note place="inline">引<note n="0899010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">六＝二【元】</note><app n="0899010"><lem wit="【大】">六</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">二</rdg></app></note>阿
<lb n="0899c05" ed="T"/>馱難尼<note place="inline">引七</note>三滿多難尼<note place="inline">引八</note>&CB00135;哩捫<note place="inline">二合</note>尼<note place="inline">引九</note>
<lb n="0899c06" ed="T"/>&CB00135;哩彌<note place="inline">二合引</note>牟<note n="0899011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00135;＝尼【明】</note><app n="0899011"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00135;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">尼</rdg></app><note place="inline">引十</note>扇<note place="inline">引</note>底莎悉爹<note place="inline">二合</note>野曩
