<lb n="0899c08" ed="T"/>同</note>叉俱嚕莎<note place="inline">引</note>賀<note place="inline">引十三</note></p>
<lb n="0899c09" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0899c0901">爾時娑婆世界主大梵天王。亦隨喜宣說寶
<lb n="0899c10" ed="T"/>帶大明曰。</p>
<lb n="0899c11" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0899c1101" type="dharani">薩拽替<note place="inline">引</note>唐<note place="inline">一<app source="0899003" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">句</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app></note>盎虞哩<note place="inline">引二</note>半虞哩<note place="inline">引三</note>阿訥
